modName: Less To Render - A performance mod
summary: A simple mod for weaker PC:s to increase frame rate.
descriptionHtml:
Okay, this is a fair simple mod. For now, removes pretty much all plants from Skyrim, giving you a boost for your frames. It is script free, and does not edit any locations, so it should not affect your saved games in any way. I used blank meshes for certain objects to make them disappear.  

I have planned to remove more insignificant stuff for game-play too.
Also FOMOD installer to pick  and a full list of removed objects is on their way. Please be patient.

(obviously) INCOMPATIBLE WITH MODS THAT EDIT PLANT MESHES\TEXTURES.

I really appreciate feedback, since this is my first mod. : )
author: Eversti97
